捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/hWh5Sax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWh5Sax.jpg&h=f682f165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Rcba2Hh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcba2Hh.png&h=a61a5d44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b054cfcf80a256536f185df0d6f38cfb42219d6","tid":1390233,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a7ac8be2928eb61096d5528ffa1cff1898bd7b","tid":1390233,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b054cfcf80a256536f185df0d6f38cfb42219d6","tid":1390233,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40be6fc17513999d638d8d6cf83b4275db23038","tid":1390233,"uid":62710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"dee柒777呀"},{"pid":"c9384bbac8623824168cb7db78ac735a30f0be75","tid":1390233,"uid":765